OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late brightness.
OL,7,FRain will spread east across all parts
OL,8,Fduring the early hours, becoming dry
OL,9,Facross the Isles later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FOutbreaks of rain will clear
OL,12,Faway east through the morning. Then
OL,13,Fthe rest of the day will bright spells
OL,14,Fand scattered showers. Colder than of
OL,15,Flate.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
